[I] Scalable Video Technology for AV1

[T] The Scalable Video Technology for AV1 (SVT-AV1 Encoder and Decoder) is an
[T] AV1-compliant encoder/decoder library core. The SVT-AV1 encoder
[T] development is a work-in-progress targeting performance levels applicable
[T] to both VOD and Live encoding / transcoding video applications.

[U] https://gitlab.com/AOMediaCodec/SVT-AV1/

